The Latin is limited. When I ordered this book I was expecting all the readings to be in Latin with English translations. I like to follow along with the priest during the Latin Mass on Sundays. I can't do that with this missal. Although it is good for the English Mass. 
I find myself still using my old 1962 version during the Latin Masses on Sundays and using this one for Weekday Masses and English Masses on Sundays. Best Uses: Weekday Masses; Cons: Limited Latin; Pros: Feels good to hold


